    "In recent years, with the development of multimedia technology and the rapid popularization of digital equipment (Graziani et al. 2022), the amount of Internet video data has grown significantly.",
    "Therefore, how to deal with these multimedia data efficiently and accurately has become a hot research topic (Le et al. 2021).",
    "The purpose of video understanding is to automatically identify and parse the content of a video using intelligent analysis technology.",
    "Given the success of deep learning in image processing and detection, researchers have introduced deep learning methods to the field of video understanding (Hutchinson and Gadepally 2021)."
